    <h1 class="title topictitle1" id="ariaid-title1">RxTx</h1>

    
    <div class="body"><p class="shortdesc">The <em class="ph i">RxTx</em> is part of the <em class="ph i">Radio Section</em> in the transceiver.</p>

        <p class="p">The <em class="ph i">RxTx</em> is connected to the RxTx controller and the SSPA. The functionality of
            the RxTx includes:</p>

        <div class="p">
            <ul class="ul">
                <li class="li">Tx up converter</li>

                <li class="li">Rx down converter</li>

                <li class="li">Frequency synthesis circuitry</li>

                <li class="li">A VCO which provides the local oscillator signals in the Rx and Tx chains</li>

                <li class="li">A Tx chain attenuator supports TX reduced transmit power in sectors</li>

                <li class="li">The RxTx provides system clock to the RxTx Controller</li>

                <li class="li">Measurement system for monitoring noise figure, forward and reverse power</li>

            </ul>

        </div>

    </div>

</body>
